        public static java.util.ArrayList<Ingredient> getUnderStockedIngredients()
        Retrieves a list of understocked ingredients from the inventory. This method scans the list of ingredients in the inventory and identifies those that have quantities below their specified restocking threshold. It returns an ArrayList of understocked ingredients.
